column5: You can build more for a while still. They say another 15cm (6"'s) on the way. More shovelling too. Yeah!
I may be the only one hoping for snow...bought a snowblower a few weeks back and she's been parked in the garage waiting for some action!
Sleigh bells ring, are you listening In the lane, snow is glistening A Beautiful Sight We're happy tonight Walking in a Winter Wonderland
Come on up and do my driveway anytime.
For two years after I bought my first blower it never snowed enough to use it  vance
